ED_Title: Financing of the United Nations Mission in East Timor
ED_DecisionText: At its 102nd plenary meeting, on 9 September 2021, the General Assembly decided to defer consideration of the item entitled “Financing of the United Nations Mission in East Timor” and to include it in the draft agenda of its seventy-sixth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/75/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
